                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">Bürger</roleName> Jorgen
                        des Neuer</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__andreas_ris_QGW_II_I_1477"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>Bürger</add></roleName>Andres des Rysen</rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="nota"><p>Indorsat: Concessi huic vidue III lib. den. antiquorum Wienn. et s( olidos) sex et 34
